ily:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;font-size:9pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">地点：吴江区人力资源市场（长安路<span>3223</span>号，人社大厦一楼）</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;font-size:9pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">三、有关要求</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;font-size:9pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、本次招聘会预设展位<span>64</span>个，用人单位免费进场，高校毕业生及市内相关求职者均可免费进场应聘求职。</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;font-size:9pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、请用人单位请根据需要制定招聘计划。</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;font-size:9pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、请参加招聘的用人单位持营业执照副本、经办人身份证复印件及招聘信息电子版到吴江区人力资源市场（长安路<span>3223</span>号人社大厦一楼）报名或将营业执照副本、经办人身份证复印件及招聘信息电子版传真邮箱。</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;font-size:9pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、请用人单位自行制作易拉宝、<span>X</span>展架等宣传海报。</span><span style=\"font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\";color:bla