serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">吴江区人力资源市场布局合理，设施齐全，功能完备。作为其载体的吴江区人力资源和社会保障服务大厦，总投资<span>3</span>个亿，总面积达<span>3</span>万平米。区人力资源市场于<span>2012</span>年<span>9</span>月正式建成投入使用，借鉴国内外多家人力资源市场的建设经验，专业规划，摊位宽敞。商务中心、网络控制、信息查询、技能测评等区域一应具有。市场招聘大厅达<span>2270</span>平米，档案室<span>80</span>平米，拥有室内室外二块大型<span>LED</span>电子显示屏，人数计数器、自助招聘摊位<span>12</span>个<span>,</span>常设招聘摊位<span>64</span>个，以及网络招聘室、视频招聘室、自助招聘摊位、面谈式招聘摊位等。实现了自助式求职招聘、摊位式洽谈招聘、网络招聘和视频招聘等功能。现将本次招聘会有关事项通知如下。</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">一、主办、承办单位</span></b><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">主办：吴江区人力资源和社会保障局</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">承办：吴江区就管中心、吴江区人力资源市场</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">二、时间、地点</span></b><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">时间：<span>6</span>月<span>3</span>日（星期二<span>8</span>：<span>30</span>―<span>12</span>：<span>00</span>）</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">地点：吴江区人力资源市场（长安路<span>3223</span>号，人社大厦一楼）</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">三、有关要求</span></b><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、本次招聘会预设展位<span>64</span>个，用人单位免费进场，高校毕业生及市内相关求职者均可免费进场应聘求职。</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、请用人单位请根据需要制定招聘计划。</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、请参加招聘的用人单位持营业执照副本、经办人身份证复印件及招聘信息电子版到吴江区人力资源市场（长安路<span>3223</span>号人社大厦一楼）报名或将营业执照副本、经办人身份证复印件及招聘信息电子版传真邮箱。</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、请用人单位自行制作易拉宝、<span>X</span>展架等宣传海报。</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">四、联系方式</span></b><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">联系人：王先生</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" Tahoma?,?sans-serif?;color:black;font-size:9pt;?></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">联系电话：<span>0512 - 88986779</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">电子邮箱：</span><span><a href=\"mailto:598431117@qq.com\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:12pt;text-decoration:none;\">598431117@qq.com</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">官方求职<span>QQ</span>群：<span>239656150</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span>','吴江区长安路3223号人社大厦一楼','王先生','0512 - 88986779','108，201路公交到[人社大厦]站即可到达','1403884800','1401120000','1403798400','17','64','1403511974','0','1','1401120000','0');
